Package: SepsisR
Type: Package
Title: A Simple Set of Functions for Data Related to Sepsis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Trent", "Gillingham", email = "trentgillin@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A set of functions that a data analyst working in health care can use to help with data related to Sepsis. The main focus of this package is to calculate three organ failure scores related to sepsis, qSOFA, SOFA, and SIRS.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
